; L11: Comprehensive Sorting关 (Final Puzzle)
; Grid: 14-col x 8-row playable (x: 0-13, y: 0-7)
; Player at (1,2), Box at (2,3) top=NORMAL_A
; Ramp at (3,3) dir=UP → rolling UP: top→front=HEAVY (NORMAL→HEAVY)
; Conveyor at (10,3) going RIGHT
; RotatingPlatform at (8,5)
; Button at (13,5) requires ENERGY
;
; Solution path: ramp→conveyor→rotating platform (multiple times) → button
; Player must cycle the box through terrain multiple times to get ENERGY face
; This is the hardest level — tests deep understanding of face rotation

[node name="Level11" type="Node3D"]
script = ExtResource("1")
start_hint_text = "综合排序关：用坡道、传送带、旋转台反复调整箱子朝向。"
completed_hint_text = "第八课完成。工厂主题全部解锁！"

